		<h2><a id="titleHref" href="/story/2013/05/09/1208068/-Heritage-s-in-house-white-supremacist-wrote-for-white-supremacists">Heritage's in-house white supremacist wrote for white supremacists</a><span style="white-space: nowrap"></span></h2>
		
		<p class="author"><span>by</span> <a href="/user/kos">kos</a><a class="ajax type-user do-hotlist do-updateContent size-tiny off altTooltip" alt="Follow this author" href="#?friend_id=3&is_stream=1">Follow</a> </p>
    
    <ul class="front-page-share clearfix">
      
      <li style="margin-left: 0px"><div class="fb-like" data-send="false" data-layout="button_count" data-width="450" data-show-faces="false" data-href="http://www.dailykos.com/story/2013/05/09/1208068/-Heritage-s-in-house-white-supremacist-wrote-for-white-supremacists"></div></li>
      <li><a href="https://twitter.com/share" class="twitter-share-button" data-count="horizontal" data-via="dailykos" data-related="markos" data-url="http://www.dailykos.com/story/2013/05/09/1208068/-Heritage-s-in-house-white-supremacist-wrote-for-white-supremacists" data-text="Heritage&#39;s in-house white supremacist wrote for white supremacists">Tweet</a></li>
          
		  <li style="margin-left: 0px"><a href="#" class="email">Email</a></li>
		  
		  <li><a href="/story/2013/05/09/1208068/-Heritage-s-in-house-white-supremacist-wrote-for-white-supremacists#comments" class="comments comment_count_with_new" data-story_id="1208068" data-comment_count="72">72 Comments</a></li>
